The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques for automatic segmentation of fetal brain in MRI images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper also discusses the real-time processing of MRI images, which can be considered as a multimedia application (cs.MM).
